OL,4,CHirwaun will be 'missed beyond measure'
OL,6,FThe family of a 13-year-old boy killed
OL,7,Fafter being hit by a car in Hirwaun
OL,8,Fhave paid tribute to their "bright,
OL,9,Fintelligent boy".
OL,11,FKaylan Hippsely died in hospital after
OL,12,Fa collision involving a Ford Fiesta in
OL,13,F, , on Thursday, 29 February.
OL,15,FIn a tribute shared by South Wales
OL,16,FPolice, his family said: "Kaylan was
OL,17,Fsuch a cheeky chappie. He always had a
OL,18,Ftwinkle in his eye and could get away
OL,19,Fwith anything with his smile and quick
OL,20,Fwit.
