OL,6,F"He was so handsome just like his dad.
OL,8,F"Kaylan was a talented rugby and
OL,9,Ffootball player. He loved online
OL,10,Fgaming.
OL,12,F"He was a bright, intelligent boy and
OL,13,Fa much-loved pupil in Aberdare
OL,14,FCommunity School.
OL,16,F"He loved spending time with his
OL,17,Ffamily and had a great group of
OL,18,Ffriends.
