OL,3,CBoy who died after being hit by car in
OL,4,CHirwaun will be 'missed beyond measure'
OL,6,F"We are devastated to lose Kaylan at
OL,7,Fsuch a young age, only 13 with his
OL,8,Fwhole life ahead of him."
OL,10,FThe family thanked those who helped
OL,11,FKaylan, saying: "We as a family want
OL,12,Fto thank everyone who helped at the
OL,13,Fscene from paramedics, members of
OL,14,Fpublic, Kaylan's friends to the
OL,15,Femergency services and police who did
OL,16,Feverything they could to save Kaylan.
OL,17,FFrom the bottom of our hearts, we are
OL,18,Fgrateful.
