OL,3,CBoy who died after being hit by car in
OL,4,CHirwaun will be 'missed beyond measure'
OL,6,F"Our thanks also go out to the local
OL,7,Fcommunity of Hirwaun who have
OL,8,Fsupported us from afar sending their
OL,9,Fprayers and support. We are very
OL,10,Fgrateful.
OL,12,F"We want to especially thank the
OL,13,Fnurses and doctors at the paediatric
OL,14,Fcritical care at the Heath Hospital
OL,15,Ffor caring for Kaylan and supporting
OL,16,Four family at such an awful time. We
OL,17,Fwill be forever grateful for their
OL,18,Fsupport.
