OL,3,CBoy who died after being hit by car in
OL,4,CHirwaun will be 'missed beyond measure'
OL,6,F"Kaylan, your life was a blessing,
OL,7,Fyour memory a treasure. You are loved
OL,8,Fbeyond words and missed beyond
OL,9,Fmeasure. Until we meet again."
OL,11,FHarley Whiteman, 19, from Hirwaun,
OL,12,Fappeared at Cardiff Magistrates' Court
OL,13,Fon Saturday, 2 March, charged with
OL,14,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,15,Fdriving and failing to provide a
OL,16,Fspecimen for analysis. He was remanded
OL,17,Fin custody and is due to appear at
OL,18,FMerthyr Crown Court later this week.
